Blast Tokens will be a valuable rewards obtained in special ways in-game, or purchased. 

Use Blast Tokens to purchase equipment on the marketplace.

Earn Blast Pass points in matches, events and
leaderboards to progress in the Blast Pass.
The pool of points for matches refreshes over time.

Gain Craft Spice by placing higher in matches using NFTs.

Craft Spice is used on the Blast Hub for upgrading, repairing
and replicating equipment.

Gain Coins by scrapping equipment.

Trophies increase your Craft Spice pool and move you higher in the Global Leadearboard.

Place higher in Battle Royale matches to earn trophies.
